ef="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-calls-out-fan-for-throwing-vape-at-him-on-stage-footage-3472463">向一名粉丝扔电子烟，并向他大声喊叫</a>。</p><p>此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink">P!nk</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-stunned-as-fan-throws-mothers-ashes-onto-stage-at-bst-hyde-park-3461977">一名粉丝将死去母亲的骨灰扔到伦敦舞台上</a>后感到困惑， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/harry-styles-hit-eye-thrown-object-vienna-concert-3466448">哈利·斯泰尔斯 (Harry Styles) 在维也纳被扔向他的神秘物体击中眼睛</a>，而<a href="https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/entertainment/a44283921/ava-max-bebe-rexha-attacked-on-stage/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">艾娃·麦克斯 (Ava Max) 则被某人打耳光。</a>在洛杉矶的一场演出中<a href="https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/entertainment/a44283921/ava-max-bebe-rexha-attacked-on-stage/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">跑上舞台</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-warns-fans-against-throwing-things-onstage-at-las-vegas-residency-3476190">凯莉·克拉克森 (Kelly Clarkson) 警告粉丝不要在拉斯维加斯驻场演出的舞台上扔东西的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
